@startuml UC-002 Driver's Daily Workflow & Live Updates
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam actor {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1976D2
  FontColor #0D47A1
}
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #E8F5E8
  BorderColor #388E3C
  FontColor #1B5E20
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3E0
  BorderColor #F57C00
  FontColor #E65100
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color #424242
}

' --- Actors ---
actor "Driver" as DR #E3F2FD
actor "Fleet Manager" as FM #E3F2FD

rectangle "UC-002: Driver's Daily Workflow & Live Updates" as UC002 {
  usecase "Log into Driver Portal" as UC1
  usecase "View Assigned Route\n(Map & Stop Order)" as UC2
  usecase "Review Route for\nNavigation & Planning" as UC3
  usecase "Receive Live Route Update\n(if modified mid-shift)" as EXT1 #FFEBEE
}

' --- Vertical flow ---
DR -down-> UC1
UC1 -down-> UC2
UC2 -down-> UC3

' --- Extension ---
EXT1 ..> UC2 : extends (live update)

' --- Manager pushes updates ---
FM --> EXT1 : modifies route

' --- Preconditions & Validation ---
note right of UC1
  **Precondition:**  
  - Dispatched route exists for the driver's shift.
end note

note right of UC2
  **Validation Criteria:**  
  - System verifies route is published  
  - Route visible to assigned driver
end note

note as N1
  **Goal:** Provide drivers with a read-only interface  
  for viewing their assigned routes.  
  **Description:** Driver receives route details (map, stop order)  
  and uses them during shift. Updates are pushed instantly  
  if the Fleet Manager changes the route.
end note

DR .. N1

@enduml
